OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTuesday deadline for       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprepayment meter action    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy companies have until Tuesday to 
OL,6, decide what action they will take for  
OL,7, customers who may have had prepayment  
OL,8, meters wrongfully installed.           
OL,10,FBusiness Secretary Grant Shapps said   
OL,11,Fenergy suppliers need to refocus their 
OL,12,Fefforts on the consumers "at the end of
OL,13,Fthis abhorrent behaviour".             
OL,15,FIt follows a series of reports about   
OL,16,Fthe forced installation of prepayment  
OL,17,Fmeters in people's homes.              
OL,19,FRegulator Ofgem said it shares Mr      
OL,20,FShapp's shock at the revelations.      
